                <head>212. Memorandum of a Conversation, White House, Washington, January 30, 1956,
                    2:15–4 p.m.<note n="1" type="source" xml:id="d212fn1">Source: Department of
                        State, Conference Files: Lot 62 D 181, <gloss target="#t_CF1">CF</gloss>
                        648. Secret. Drafted on February 7. No other drafting information is given
                        on the source text. Prime Minister <persName corresp="#p_ERHSA1"
                            >Eden</persName> visited Washington January 30–February 3.</note>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#left">
                        <gloss target="#t_ETW1">ETW</gloss>
                        <gloss target="#t_MC1">MC</gloss>–1</seg>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
